Title: Lego DC Comics Super Heroes: The Flash
Writer: James Krieg, Jeremy Adams, Jerry Siegel (character created by: Superman), Joe Shuster (character created by: Superman), Paul Norris (character created by: Aquaman), Gardner Fox (character created by: Atom/Ray Palmer), Bob Kane (character created by: Batman), Bill Finger (character created by: Batman), Marv Wolfman (character created by: Cyborg), George Pérez (character created by: Cyborg), Gardner Fox (character created by: Doctor Fate), Gerry Conway (character created by: Firestorm), Al Milgrom (character created by: Firestorm), Gerry Conway (character created by: Killer Croc), Don Newton (character created by: Killer Croc), Jack Cole (character created by: Plastic Man), William Moulton Marston (character created by: Wonder Woman), Gardner Fox (character created by: Zatanna), Murphy Anderson (character created by: Zatanna)

Plot: Reverse-Flash manipulates the Speed Force to put The Flash into a time loop, which forces him to re-live the same day over and over again. The Flash must find a way to restore time and finally apprehend his worst enemy before all is lost.
